{
  "$comment": [
    "Differential corpus for the partitioned write APPLIER (job-dispatcher.ts",
    "applyWritesUnsafe + applyPartition + applySecondaryBestEffort +",
    "applyFolderCreateIdempotent), ported to quilltap-core::write_apply.",
    "",
    "This layer is pure ORCHESTRATION — partition by target DB, per-partition",
    "transaction lifecycle, main-primary vs idempotent ordering + failure policy,",
    "and the concurrent-folder-create reconcile. v4 unit-tests it with fake DBs +",
    "recording repos (no real DB); the actual row writes are delegated to repos,",
    "each tier-2-verified on its own. So this is a tier-1-style TRACE differential,",
    "not a tier-2 DB-state diff.",
    "",
    "Both sides run this same corpus and emit the same observable trace per",
    "scenario: per-partition exec sequence (BEGIN IMMEDIATE / COMMIT / ROLLBACK),",
    "the ordered list of ATTEMPTED repo dispatches (method + args, args POST folder",
    "remap), the reconcile lookups, and the resolved/threw outcome. jobId = the",
    "scenario name on both sides (it appears in the connection-unavailable message).",
    "",
    "The trace also captures the __finalizeFile + post-commit effects: renames",
    "(ordered {from,to} across the in-transaction staging rename AND the reverse",
    "undo on rollback), mkdirs (ensureDir(dirname(finalPath))), rms (the post-commit",
    "cleanupStagingDirs root), and notifications (the deduped dispatchInvalidations",
    "targets, {kind: vectorStore|mountPoint, key}). On the oracle side these come",
    "from fs mutator spies (rename/mkdir/rm) + the notifyChild mock.",
    "",
    "fail[].message is the error a dispatch throws; both sides use it verbatim so",
    "the threw-outcome string matches. findFolder maps a (mountPointId, path) to the",
    "existing folder id the reconcile resolves to (null => no row). unavailable",
    "lists partitions whose connection is null; failCommit lists partitions whose",
    "COMMIT throws. A __finalizeFile write carries {stagingPath, finalPath} in",
    "args[0]; it is intercepted (never dispatched to a repo)."
  ],
  "scenarios": [
    {
      "name": "idempotent-mixed-isolates-and-orders",
      "jobType": "EMBEDDING_GENERATE",
      "writes": [
        { "method": "chats.update", "args": [{ "id": "c1" }] },
        { "method": "docMountChunks.updateEmbedding", "args": [{ "id": "ch1" }] },
        { "method": "embeddingStatus.markAsEmbedded", "args": [{ "id": "ch1" }] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "idempotent-secondary-fails-never-touches-main",
      "jobType": "EMBEDDING_GENERATE",
      "writes": [
        { "method": "chats.update", "args": [{ "id": "c1" }] },
        { "method": "docMountChunks.updateEmbedding", "args": [{ "id": "ch1" }] }
      ],
      "fail": [{ "method": "docMountChunks.updateEmbedding", "message": "mount boom" }]
    },
    {
      "name": "autonomous-secondary-fails-keeps-chat",
      "jobType": "AUTONOMOUS_ROOM_TURN",
      "writes": [
        { "method": "chats.addMessage", "args": [{ "id": "m1" }] },
        { "method": "chats.update", "args": [{ "id": "c1", "runState": "idle" }] },
        { "method": "docMountChunks.updateEmbedding", "args": [{ "id": "ch1" }] }
      ],
      "fail": [{ "method": "docMountChunks.updateEmbedding", "message": "mount degraded" }]
    },
    {
      "name": "autonomous-main-fails-aborts-before-secondary",
      "jobType": "AUTONOMOUS_ROOM_TURN",
      "writes": [
        { "method": "chats.addMessage", "args": [{ "id": "m1" }] },
        { "method": "docMountFolders.create", "args": [{ "mountPointId": "MP", "path": "foo", "parentId": null, "name": "foo" }, { "id": "F1" }] }
      ],
      "fail": [{ "method": "chats.addMessage", "message": "main boom" }]
    },
    {
      "name": "folder-create-reconcile-remaps-refs",
      "jobType": "EMBEDDING_GENERATE",
      "writes": [
        { "method": "docMountFolders.create", "args": [{ "mountPointId": "MP", "path": "foo", "parentId": null, "name": "foo" }, { "id": "BUF" }] },
        { "method": "docMountFileLinks.create", "args": [{ "mountPointId": "MP", "folderId": "BUF", "relativePath": "foo/x.md" }, { "id": "L1" }] }
      ],
      "fail": [{ "method": "docMountFolders.create", "message": "UNIQUE constraint failed: doc_mount_folders", "code": "SQLITE_CONSTRAINT_UNIQUE" }],
      "findFolder": [{ "mountPointId": "MP", "path": "foo", "result": "EXIST" }]
    },
    {
      "name": "folder-create-unique-no-existing-surfaces",
      "jobType": "EMBEDDING_GENERATE",
      "writes": [
        { "method": "docMountFolders.create", "args": [{ "mountPointId": "MP", "path": "foo", "parentId": null, "name": "foo" }, { "id": "BUF" }] }
      ],
      "fail": [{ "method": "docMountFolders.create", "message": "UNIQUE constraint failed", "code": "SQLITE_CONSTRAINT_UNIQUE" }],
      "findFolder": [{ "mountPointId": "MP", "path": "foo", "result": null }]
    },
    {
      "name": "llm-logs-only-batch",
      "jobType": "LLM_LOG_CLEANUP",
      "writes": [
        { "method": "llmLogs.cleanupOldLogs", "args": [30] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "connection-unavailable-throws",
      "jobType": "EMBEDDING_GENERATE",
      "writes": [
        { "method": "docMountChunks.updateEmbedding", "args": [{ "id": "ch1" }] }
      ],
      "unavailable": ["mountIndex"]
    },
    {
      "name": "idempotent-main-commit-fails-rolls-back",
      "jobType": "EMBEDDING_GENERATE",
      "writes": [
        { "method": "chats.update", "args": [{ "id": "c1" }] }
      ],
      "failCommit": [{ "partition": "main", "message": "commit boom" }]
    },
    {
      "name": "finalize-success-then-cleanup",
      "jobType": "EMBEDDING_GENERATE",
      "writes": [
        { "method": "__finalizeFile", "args": [{ "stagingPath": "/data/files/.staging/finalize-success-then-cleanup/aa/note.md", "finalPath": "/data/files/store/aa/note.md" }] },
        { "method": "chats.update", "args": [{ "id": "c1" }] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "finalize-rollback-undoes-renames",
      "jobType": "EMBEDDING_GENERATE",
      "writes": [
        { "method": "__finalizeFile", "args": [{ "stagingPath": "/d/.staging/finalize-rollback-undoes-renames/s1", "finalPath": "/d/store/f1" }] },
        { "method": "__finalizeFile", "args": [{ "stagingPath": "/d/.staging/finalize-rollback-undoes-renames/s2", "finalPath": "/d/store/f2" }] },
        { "method": "chats.update", "args": [{ "id": "c1" }] }
      ],
      "fail": [{ "method": "chats.update", "message": "rollback boom" }]
    },
    {
      "name": "invalidations-dedup-across-batch",
      "jobType": "EMBEDDING_GENERATE",
      "writes": [
        { "method": "memories.create", "args": [{ "characterId": "charX" }] },
        { "method": "memories.delete", "args": [{ "characterId": "charX" }] },
        { "method": "vectorIndices.saveMeta", "args": [{ "characterId": "charY" }] },
        { "method": "docMountChunks.upsert", "args": [{ "mountPointId": "MP" }] },
        { "method": "chats.update", "args": [{ "characterId": "charZ" }] }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
